Hey! Why are you riding so fast?

28
00:02:49,690 --> 00:02:51,650
Hey! Did you hear?

29
00:02:51,650 --> 00:02:54,460
Grade Eleven is getting a transfer student.

30
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:56,540
- Really?
- Yeah.

31
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:02,590
Don't know if it's a girl or a boy. What's your guess?

32
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:04,830
I'm guessing...

33
00:03:04,830 --> 00:03:07,690
You're already in the Twelfth grade, can't you be a bit more mature?

34
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:10,280
What did you get on the mock test last time?

35
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:13,910
It would be awesome if it was a really cute girl.

36
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:17,720
Our school has too few pretty girls.

37
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:20,420
Don't you think so? Hey, Liang Younian!

38
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:22,340
Wait for me!

39
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:25,550
Mr. Zhang and Mrs. Li, I'll visit you both when I have time.

40
00:03:25,550 --> 00:03:26,760
Okay.

41
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:30,450
Xia Miaomiao! What are you doing? Hurry!

42
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:47,180
Oh, my. Slowly, slowly.

43
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:51,300
This girl. Hang on, Mom's going to help you.

44
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:54,710
Your father really is something. He didn't even wait for us to finish moving first before going out to the sea again.

45
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:56,600
What is he in such a hurry for?

46
00:03:56,600 --> 00:04:00,110
Dad said that the sea is the sailor's clock.

47
00:04:00,110 --> 00:04:04,750
Sure, sure, sure. Your father is the most worthy of admiration in your heart.

48
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:07,170
Xia Yao Yao! Hurry up!

49
00:04:07,170 --> 00:04:08,990
I almost forgot about you.

50
00:04:08,990 --> 00:04:10,790
Coming!

51
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:31,760
I've finished moving everything.

52
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:36,100
Boss, we're neighbors from now on, so let's take care of each other.

53
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:39,310
It's just a little messy. It'll be better in just a bit.

54
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:44,310
