56
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:50,120
Will anyone be able to find the store?

57
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,450
As long as the wine is good, there's no reason to fear a long alley.

58
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:57,780
Besides, the balcony on the second floor has a view of the lighthouse.

59
00:04:57,820 --> 00:05:01,670
Haven't we been able to see a lighthouse every time we've moved?

60
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:04,900
