66
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,390
- Boss!
- Yes?

67
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:32,070
Congrats on moving to a new house. This is for you.

68
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:34,180
Thank you, thank you!

69
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:37,140
Come eat when you have time, I'll give you a discount!

70
00:05:37,180 --> 00:05:38,880
Mom.

71
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:41,790
