76
00:05:52,730 --> 00:05:54,820
Mrs. Xia's Private Kitchen

77
00:06:07,860 --> 00:06:13,460
Xiao Yaoyao! It's fine if you're not helping, but you're making a mess. Pick it up.

78
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:15,230
No.

79
00:06:19,340 --> 00:06:22,660
Did you hear what I said? Mom will get mad again.

80
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:27,510
Hey! Let see you try and dodge my grapefruit dart!

81
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,990
- You missed!
- Just you wait, you're dead meat!

82
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,000
Oh, no. Oh, no.

