It's fine.

85
00:06:43,690 --> 00:06:46,020
Big Brother.

86
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:49,060
Sorry. Are you okay?

87
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:33,160
Menu

88
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,180
Mom.

