Stop!

152
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:33,000
Stop!

153
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,700
Take off that uniform.

154
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:48,800
You're still the same.

155
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:52,000
