167
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,200
Ah Xia!

168
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,600
Miaomiao!

169
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:08,400
I miss you so much. Now that you're gone, there's no one to accompany me to the bathroom anymore.

170
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:10,300
I miss you so much, too.

171
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,800
Let me tell you something.

172
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:18,600
