175
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:29,200
There's someone called Lin Kaituo.

176
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,600
I think he's on the basketball team.

177
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,910
Lin Kaituo?

178
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:36,000
[HDFZ Campus Forum]

179
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,800
The Seven Sins of the Devil Incarnate, Lin Kaituo of HDFZ

180
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:51,400
Today, I walked by the basketball court and a girl tried to hand a bottle of water to Lin Kaituo, captain of the basketball team.

181
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:53,600
