197
00:17:58,570 --> 00:18:00,760
My leg hurts.

198
00:18:02,010 --> 00:18:03,750
Does it hurt here?

199
00:18:05,390 --> 00:18:07,250
Can you stand?

200
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:14,900
Big Brother will do a magic trick for you. Wait here.

201
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,800
One, two, three.

202
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:35,400
Be a bit more careful next time, okay? Also, don't be so noisy. Off you go.

203
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:27,100
What?

204
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,800
