210
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:04,900
- Oh, Uncle.
- Yes?

211
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:06,580
This...

212
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,200
will be on Dachao's tab.

213
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:10,000
- Dachao?
- Yes.

214
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:16,670
